WEBVTT


00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:24.020
Now that I saw you,

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:27.440
don't wanna think of anything else.

00:00:27.441 --> 00:00:28.981
Now that I thought of you,

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:02.640
maybe you ran with the wolves and refused to settle down.

00:01:02.641 --> 00:01:05.121
Maybe I stormed out of every single room in this town,

00:01:05.122 --> 00:01:07.801
threw out our clothes and our daggers because it's morning now.

00:01:07.802 --> 00:01:11.221
It's brighter now. Now I don't wanna look in.

00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:30.500
They are, they say they are. They say they like.
